{"tid":1511891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣大台已經出現","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T16:53:42.000Z","uid":238660,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7784ad231b5c74eb66d57990b2125add48b57735","tid":1511891,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"同你哋講啲好笑嘅野。<br />\n話說呢黃大仙之前呢有個文宣嘅群組<br />\n咁嗰陣時呢 大家放映嘅設備都唔係咁好<br />\n所以就大家一齊慢慢努力去盡量做到最好啦<br />\n<br />\n不過一開始嗰陣時已經留意到有手足想做大台 所以我哋當然就無理佢啦 <br />\n<br />\n咁之後我哋設備越嚟越好嗰陣時 同埋物資越來越多嗰陣時 佢就偷偷地自己開咗個細群組 叫走晒我哋啲人 咁嗰陣時我已經發現到㗎啦 <br />\n<br />\n已經同左其他人講 但係嗰陣時其他人都覺得大家都係想搞好文宣啫<br />\n<br />\n直到今日 問題大左好多 叫走晒啲人都算啦 連最基本嘅禮貌都冇埋 我哋有手足想過去幫手 佢就話你唔好過嚟啦 仲要限制埋人哋可唔可以去 最嬲就係去到 嗰邊搞緊嘅人唔係佢 佢一早已經離開咗現場 但係唔俾其他人去 嘗試了解嗰陣時 仲可以叫人托柒"},{"pid":"8d5c6c731a5445837d7460f4e55636a9a4a65054","tid":1511891,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suRKmvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRKmvs.gif&h=09fb3e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=692b68d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=002b3d78\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a